1. Create Zmass study histograms root file:
================================
Wpt study
================================
root -l -b -q WPtZmassMakeHisto.C

================================
Zpt study
================================
root.exe -b
.x ZPtZmassMakeHisto.C++

2. Draw pT binning histograms

================================
Wpt study
================================
python Wpt_ZmassCompPtBins_Gaus.py

================================
Zpt study
================================
python Zpt_ZmassCompPtBins_Gaus.py

3. Draw eta binning histograms

================================
Wpt study
================================
python Wpt_ZmassCompEtaBins_Gaus.py

================================
Zpt study
================================
python Zpt_ZmassCompEtaBins_Gaus.py

4. Draw muon pT histograms
Wpt_muPtComp.py

5. Draw different regions (Total,BB,BE,EE) histograms
================================
Wpt study
================================
python Wpt_ZmassComp_Gaus.py

================================
Zpt study
================================
python Zpt_ZmassComp_Gaus.py
